<st>
Personal life</st>
<p>

Drago was born <b>William Eugene Burrows</b> in <village wordnetid="108672738" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../959/114959.xml">
Hugoton, Kansas</link></village>
 to William and Gladys Burrows. His father was part <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../584/358584.xml">
Apache</link> while his mother was part <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../716/4716.xml">
Bohemian</link> and <ethnic_group wordnetid="107967382" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../512/59512.xml">
Serbian</link></ethnic_group>
 in ancestry. He took his grandmother's maiden name as his <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../412/53412.xml">
stage name</link> to keep from being confused with another actor. After high school he worked as a <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../832/313832.xml">
stuntman</link> at <site wordnetid="108651247" confidence="0.8">
