<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../893/2796893.xml">
Darren E. Burrows</link></actor>
. His wife is actress <actor wordnetid="109765278" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../398/4585398.xml">
Silvana Gallardo</link></actor>
.</p>

